  <brief_title>Hydration and Contrast-Induced Nephropathy in Primary Angioplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hydration and Contrast-Induced Nephropathy in Primary Angioplasty. A Randomized, Placebo Controlled, Trial.</official_title>
